data.description: Introducing a gorgeously updated, upgraded, and expanded 5 bedroom home nestled in the beautiful Timber Ridge subdivision. With spacious bedrooms and 4 full baths, this home boasts ample living space. An outside kitchen set up with both hot and cold water as well as natural gas set up makes entertaining your guests easy while sitting in the screened back porch or next to the fire pit and beautiful koi pond and water feature right by your mature fruit trees. There is an on demand water heater large enough to supply 4 bathrooms. Your dream kitchen includes a pot filler mounted over a gas stove that has quick boil and crab pot sized burners, appliance cabinets, custom stepstool storage cabinet, and an amazing pantry with extra storage space! Master closet is set up to organize and keep all of your things as well as having an extra closet for safe storage. Gates on both side of your property are reinforced and large enough for you to park your boat or RV on the gravel drive safely in the backyard. The beautiful shutters are fully functional and the 10000 watt generator stays with the home. Seriously, do not miss your chance to make this your forever home!
